  10,78,"qal fireawn wmlwh lmwsa: 'ajitana ltsrfna eamaa wajadna ealayh aba'ana min eibadat ghyr allh, watakun lakuma 'ant waharun alezmt walsltan fi 'ard \"msr\"? wama nahn lakuma bmqrrin bankma rswlan 'ursltma 'ilyna; linaebud allah wahdah la sharik lh"
  10,79,"wqal frewn: jyywny bikuli sahir mtqn llshr"
