  11,33,"qal nuh lqwmh: 'iina allah wahdah hu aldhy yatikum bialeadhab 'iidha sha', walastum bfaytyh 'iidha 'arad 'an yedhbkm; li'anah subhanah la yejzh shay' fi al'ard wala fi alsma'"
