  11,54,"ma naqul 'iilaa 'an baed alihatina 'asabak bjnwn bsbb nhyk ean ebadtha. qal lhm: 'iiniy 'ushhd allah ealaa ma aqwl, w'ushhdkm ealaa 'anani bari' mimaa tshrkwn, min dun allah min alandad walasnam, fanzuruu wajthdu 'antum wman zaeamtum min alihatakum fi 'iilhaq aldarar by, thuma la twkhru dhlk trft eyn; dhlk 'ana hwdana wathiq kl alwuthuq 'anah la ysybh minhum wala min alihatuhum adha"
