  11,61,"warslna 'iilaa thamud 'akhahum salhana, faqal lhm: ya qawm aebuduu allah wahdah lays lakum min 'ilh yastahiqu alebadt ghyrh jl wela, fakhlsu lah alebadt, hu aldhy bada khalqkm min al'ard bikhalq 'abikum adam mnha, wajaealakum eummara lha, fasalwh 'ana yaghfir lakum dhnwbkm, warjieuu 'iilayh baltwbt alnswh. 'iina rabiy qarib liman akhls lah alebadt, wrghb 'iilayh fi altwbt, mujib lah 'iidha deah"
