  11,73,"qalt alrusul lha: 'ataejabin min 'amr allah wqdayh? rahmat allah wabarakatuh ealaykum maeshar 'ahl bayt alnbw. 'iinah subhanah wteala hamid alsfat walafeal, dhu majd wezmt fyha"
