  11,78,"wja' qwm lut ysrewn almshy 'iilayh litalab alfahsht, wakanuu min qabl mjyyhm yatun alrijal shahwatan dun alnsa', faqal lut lqwmh: hwla' banati tazawwajwhn fhnn 'athar lakum mimaa trydwn, wsmahn bnath; li'ana nabiin al'umat bmnzlt alab lhm, fakhshu allah wahdharuu eqabh, wala tfdhwny bialaietida' ealaa dyfy, 'alays minkum rajul dhu rshd, ynha man 'arad rukub alfahsht, fyhwl baynahum wabayn dhlk?"
  11,79,"qal qawm lut lh: laqad elmt min qbl 'anah lays lana fi alnisa' min hajat 'aw rghbt, wa'iinak lataelam ma nryd, 'aya la nurid 'iilaa alrijal wala raghbat lana fi nkah alnsa'"
