  16,97,"man eamil eamalana salhana dhkrana kan 'am antha, wahu mumin biallah wrswlh, falanuhyianah fi aldunya hayat saeidat mtmynt, walaw kan qalil almal, wlnjzynnahm fi alakhirat thwabhm bi'ahsan ma eamiluu fi aldnya"
