  16,107,"'inma yaftari alkadhib man ntq bikalimat alkufr wartdd baed 'iymanh, faealayhim ghadab min allh, 'iilaa man 'urghm ealaa alntq balkfr, fntq bih khwfana min alhlak waqalbih thabt ealaa al'iyman, fala lwm elyh, lkn min ntq bialkufr watman qalbah 'ilyh, faealayhim ghadab shadid min allh, walahum eadhab ezym; wdhlk bsbb 'iytharhm aldunya wzyntha, wtfdylhm 'iyaha ealaa alakhirat wthwabha, wa'ana allah la yahdi alkafryn, wala ywfqhm lilhaqi walswab"
