  16,125,"ade -ayha alrswl- 'ant wman atabaeak 'iilaa din rabik wtryqh almstqym, bialtariqat alhakimat alty awhaha allah 'iilayk fi alkitab walsnt, wkhatib alnaas balaslwb almunasib lhm, wa'ansah lahum nshana hsnana, yrghbhm fi alkhyr, wynfrhm min alshr, wajadilhum bi'ahsan turuq almjadlt min alrfq wallyn. fama ealayk 'iilaa alblagh, waqad bllaghta, 'amaa hdaythm faealaa allah whdh, fahu 'aelam biman dll ean sbylh, wahu 'aelam balmhtdyn"
